==English==
===Etymology===
French and Old French '''machine''', from Latin '''[[machina]]''', borrowed from Ancient Greek '''[[μηχανή]]''' (probably via a dialect variant such as [[w:Doric Greek|Doric Greek]] '''[[μαχανά]]''').

